## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="846f7-124">Il est recommandé de toujours fermer une instance <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> en appelant <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.Close%2A> lorsque vous avez fini de l'utiliser.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="846f7-124">You should always close a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer> instance by calling <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageBuffer.Close%2A> when finished working with it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="846f7-125">Cela permet aux ressources système de pouvoir être éventuellement libérées plus tôt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="846f7-125">This allows system resources to potentially be freed sooner.</span></span>  
  
